<div class="home-video-wrapper">
  <%= video_tag "banner_video_blur.mp4", autoplay: :autoplay, loop: :loop, muted: :muted, class: "home_video", poster: "poster.jpg" %>
  <div class="container d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
    <div class="whitesq">
      <h1>A NEW WAY TO PRACTICE FRENCH</h1>
      <p>Join our community of <%= User.count %> French learners</p>
      <%= link_to "FREE TRIAL", plan_path(Plan.find_by(sku: 'curieux')), class: "btn btn-primary", style: "width: 300px;"  %>
    </div>
    <div id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly" class="carousel slide container text-center responsive-hidden" data-ride="carousel" style="position: absolute; bottom: 30px; opacity: .8; color: white;">
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active" data-interval="7000">
          <p><em>
            "I am glad that I found this group with Nelly, it has been very helpful.
            I am grateful to Nelly for being so patient; bringing materials and resources that will benefit us.
            I am happy to add The French Cloud to my french journey!"
          </em>
          <br>
          <strong>
            Maia, USA, 27 years old, level of French A2
          </strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item" data-interval="7000">
            <p>
            <em>
              “I really like this group because we learn by communicating live with other persons and correct each other when we are wrong.
              Also it's fun to understand and memorize words or structures in context (either movies, music or books)“
            </em>
            <br>
            <strong>
              Alex, Romania, 24 years old, level of French B1
            </strong>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item" data-interval="7000">
          <p>
            <em>
              “I'm glad I found this club.
              It is really helpful to improve your french.
              Our teacher Nelly is wonderful and really patient with us.
              Also, we come to know people of different cultures from different parts of the world!
              Everyone, including our teacher, is really friendly here."
            </em>
            <br>
            <strong>
              Ankan, India, 19 years old, level of French A2/B1
            </strong>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container my-5">
  <h2>Why join the club?</h2>
  <div class="key-selling-points">
    <div class="ksp">
      <%= image_tag "humanity.png", alt: "community", width: 125 %>
      <p>A community of motivated and friendly French learners from all around the world</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ksp">
      <%= image_tag "teacher.png", alt: "certified teachers", width: 125 %>
      <p>Certified French teachers to answer all your questions, suggest exercises and correct your mistakes</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ksp">
      <%= image_tag "conversation.png", alt: "conversation sessions", width: 125 %>
      <p>Online conversation sessions every week in small groups of level lead by teachers</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h2 class="my-5" id="month-sessions">Sessions of the month</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <%= image_tag "november-planning-curieux.png", alt: "Planning of the month: November 2020 (Le curieux)", style: 'width: 100%;' %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <%= image_tag "november-planning-ptit-french.png", alt: "Planning of the month: November 2020 (Le p'tit French)", style: 'width: 100%;' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
